## Summary

This documentation covers the `@supertokens-plugins/tenant-discovery-react` plugin that provides React components and utilities for multi-tenant authentication with tenant discovery functionality, including subdomain-based tenant extraction, email-based tenant discovery, and tenant selector UI components.

